game.name: Galaxy Fleet Time Travel
game.description:
The wonderful adventure challenge has just come for you. Join Galaxy Fleet Time Travel and allow yourself to play the role of a Star Trek adventurer in space alone! You will have plenty of missions to complete and unlock seven characters like Star Lord, Spacetime Traveler, Mystery, Robot, Alone, Star Alliance members and Space Thieves. Do not forget to grab the gold coins to make your character strong in this one of the best adventure games for kids! It will be exciting to use various random props and equipment. 

In easy mode, you will meet an enemy with only a few powers, and three galaxie levels to explore with no final boss. Once you finish the game, a display will appear showing you details about the distance, highscore, your kills, playcount, and get level. Remember every character has unique abilities so try to go for a character that suits your game. You will get some initial plans every time you begin your game. Each equipment is designed to affect the special attributes. Join this war challenge as a roaming adventurer who loves to explore the space!


Check out the handbook storage skills, enemies, boss, and equipments in my data! In the achievement portion, you will be able to see all the achievements you have obtained so far. Feel free to skip the irrelevant steps and try to play as per the last section! Complete your game and obtain experience and you will soon be able to see your growing star rank! It will be amazing to look into and apply the more functions once you reach at the target rank. You need energy to go to planet. Good luck to accomplish all missions in this cool html5 space games.
